snippet.title: La Pucelle: Ragnarok (PSP) First Trailer!
snippet.description:
La Pucelle: Ragnarok (PSP) First Trailer!

The game will be released in Japan 26th November 2009. Okay N1, keep the awesome PSP ports coming.
